Package: myR
Title: Comprehensive Tools for scRNAseq (Seurat) and GeoMx Analysis
Version: 0.2.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Jaecheon", "Ko", , "eaoaeaoa@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = ".."))
Description: Provides comprehensive helper functions for single-cell RNA-seq analysis, 
    GeoMx Digital Spatial Profiling, and other multi-omics data. Includes modules for 
    quality control, differential expression, marker gene analysis, trajectory inference, 
    cell-cell communication (NicheNet), pathway enrichment, gene signature discovery, 
    and advanced visualizations. Refactored for improved modularity and maintainability.
